Resource Profile: FrPractitionerRegul

Official URL: https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/sas/StructureDefinition/FrPractitionerRegul Version: 1.0.0
Active as of 2024-10-24 Computable Name: FrPractitionerRegul

: contained.contained.empty()
